      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/sqa-level2",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) is subject to a documented software quality assurance plan conforming to FDA guidance on computer software assurance. Version control (Git with signed commits), regression test suite (487 test cases, 100% pass rate), issue tracking, and change control procedures are all in place and audited. SQA audit records confirm all Level 2 requirements met; additional Level 3 evidence includes formal code review records and third-party static analysis results. Achieved level 3 exceeds the required level 2 for MRL 3.",
