      "rationale": "A three-level grid refinement study was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at all 5 COU operating points. Grid Convergence Index (GCI) computed per Celik et al. (2008). GCI_fine for NIH: 2.3% (nominal), range 1.9–3.1% across all operating points. Apparent order of convergence p=1.87 confirms asymptotic regime. Temporal discretization error assessed via time-step refinement (Δt = 0.5°, 1°, 2° impeller rotation): NIH variation <0.8% between finest two steps. Combined space-time discretization error budget: 3.4%. This meets the Level 3 acceptance criterion of GCI < 5% and documented convergence order.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/gci-study-2025-10",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/synth/uq/gci-discretization-error-estimate"
