      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/validation-relevance-level3",
      "rationale": "Validation activities were conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which shares key non-dimensional parameters (specific speed Ns=1820, flow coefficient Φ=0.08–0.14, Reynolds number Re=1.2–2.1×10⁵) with the COU device. Operating conditions in the validation campaign span the full COU operating envelope. Fluid properties match COU conditions (blood analog at 37°C). Geometric similarity is high (same pump archetype). A formal similarity assessment table documents parameter-by-parameter comparison between validation configuration and COU. The Level 3 criterion — validation activities conducted at conditions directly relevant to the COU with documented similarity analysis — is satisfied.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/validation-relevance-review-2025-10"
